h2.div: A new collection can be described (i.e. via a form) and registered.

div.style: font-size: 12px ; font-weight: 400

h2.div: It is possible to register new members, that did not exist before, as an FDO AND after that add them to a collection. A mass ingest allows adding many FDOs as members of a collection.

div.style: font-size: 12px ; font-weight: 400

h2.div: It is possible to add an existing PID to a collection.
